title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 29 2022

description:
Joe Rogan and Aaron Rodgers teeing off on NFL vax stooges is fantastic. If those in charge of the covid response aren't held accountable, lockdowns and mandates will happen again. What is the best pitch for the 2022 midterms? To many Democrats, Biden student loan bribe doesn't go far enough. Here’s the winning GOP argument for a November reckoning. Dr. Leana Wen’s poor covid judgment is on the ballot. If your co-workers are "quiet quitting," here’s what that means. Some Gen Z professionals are saying no to hustle culture; "I’m not going to go extra."
